Navigation
Move cursor up: k
Move cursor down: j
Move cursor left: h
Move cursor right: l
Move to the beginning of a line: 0
Move to the end of a line: $
Move to the top of the file: gg
Move to the bottom of the file: G


Delete text:

Delete a character: x
Delete a word: dw
Delete a line: dd

Saving Files
Save changes: :w
Save as another name: :w newfilename
Save and exit: :wq
